      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Thomas Kolarik</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:251px;\"><a href=\"/File:ThomasKolarik.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/e/e2/ThomasKolarik.jpg\" width=\"249\" height=\"395\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:ThomasKolarik.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Thomas Kolarik <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Thomas Kolarik</b>,<br />\nan American graduated physicist from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Maryland,_Baltimore_County\">University of Maryland, Baltimore County</a>, system analyst, part time <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tennis\">tennis</a> instructor <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> , and author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/Nirvanachess\" title=\"Nirvanachess\">Nirvanachess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> . With some interests in playing chess, he started Nirvanachess as a side project in his Freshman year of college in about 2010, with the motivation to learn <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a>/<a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a> and to start a project that would keep him occupied for a while. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2012_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2012 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Kolarik&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2012_...\">2012 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Kolarik&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2012 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46605\">Move Ordering?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Kolarik</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 28, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47750\">Nirvanachess 1.0 Release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Kolarik</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 10, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48252\">A Materialless Evaluation?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Kolarik</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 12, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50476\">Test Position</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Kolarik</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 13, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53859\">Transposition Table Oddity</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Kolarik</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 28, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Kolarik&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57948\">Nirvanachess 2.2 Release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Kolarik</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58298&amp;start=43\">Re: Why computing K that minimizes the sigmoid func. value?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Kolarik</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 27, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61229\">Value of IID</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Kolarik</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 25, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Kolarik&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://nirvanachess.blogspot.com/\">Nirvanachess</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Kolarik&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Thomas Kolarik at UMBC, Photo Courtesy Thomas Kolarik, October 16, 2015</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.phys.psu.edu/people/gdm12\">Gerald D. Mahan</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://press.princeton.edu/titles/8965.html\">Quantum Mechanics in a Nutshell</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Princeton_University_Press\">Princeton University Press</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.umbc.edu/studentlife/orgs/tennis/ladders.htm\">UMBC Club Tennis</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://nirvanachess.blogspot.com/\">Nirvanachess</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301043442\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.015 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 79/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 170/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:3955-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301043442 and revision id 22055\n -->\n"
